---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About SF Bikeways" description="Discovering San Francisco's bike infrastructure, one ride at a time.">
  <div class="space-y-24">
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-medium">About SF Bikeways</h1>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]/80 text-lg">
          Welcome to SF Bikeways, your guide to exploring San Francisco by bicycle. This blog is dedicated to documenting and celebrating the city's bike infrastructure, from the famous Wiggle to hidden neighborhood routes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium">Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[var(--color-text)]/10"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]/60 leading-relaxed">
        We believe that cycling is more than just a mode of transportationâ€”it's a way to experience the city's unique character, connect with local communities, and discover hidden gems that you might miss when traveling by car. Through detailed route reviews, coffee shop recommendations, and gear insights, we aim to make cycling in San Francisco more accessible and enjoyable for everyone.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium">What We Cover</h2>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[var(--color-text)]/10"></div>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text)]/60">
        <li><strong>Route Reviews</strong>: Detailed explorations of San Francisco's bike lanes and paths</li>
        <li><strong>Coffee Shop Stops</strong>: Reviews of bike-friendly cafes and coffee shops</li>
        <li><strong>Gear Reviews</strong>: Insights on bikes, accessories, and photography equipment</li>
        <li><strong>Infrastructure Updates</strong>: News about new bike lanes and improvements</li>
        <li><strong>Local Cycling Events</strong>: Coverage of community rides and cycling events</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium">Join the Journey</h2>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[var(--color-text)]/10"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]/60 leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're a seasoned cyclist or just getting started, we invite you to join us in exploring San Francisco's bike infrastructure. Follow along as we document our rides, share our experiences, and help build a more bike-friendly city.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]/60 leading-relaxed">
        Feel free to reach out with route suggestions, coffee shop recommendations, or just to say hello!
      </p>
      
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout> 